OL,3,CHow heatwaves are changing the face of
OL,4,CBritain
OL,6,FHere, ITV News Science Correspondent
OL,7,FMartin Stew speaks to citrus growers,
OL,8,Fthe head of an air conditioning
OL,9,Fbusiness and a climate scientist about
OL,10,Fhow increasingly hotter summers are
OL,11,Fchanging life in Britain.
OL,13,FWords by Health and Science Producer
OL,14,FRhiannon Hopley
OL,16,FYou may have noticed that the weather
OL,17,Fin the UK is changing.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
