OL,3,CHow heatwaves are changing the face of
OL,4,CBritain
OL,6,FParts of Britain are experiencing
OL,7,Ftheir fourth heatwave of the year,
OL,8,Fwith temperatures breaching 30C in
OL,9,Fsome places.
OL,11,FHot days like this are becoming the
OL,12,Fnorm in the UK.
OL,14,FThe last three years have ranked among
OL,15,Fthe warmest on record, with annual
OL,16,Ftemperatures creeping up at a rate of
OL,17,F0.25C per decade since the 1980s.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
