OL,3,CHow heatwaves are changing the face of
OL,4,CBritain
OL,6,FExtremes are also becoming more usual
OL,7,F- last year was one of the wettest on
OL,8,Frecord, while spring 2025 was the
OL,9,Fdriest in 132 years.
OL,11,FSo how does the UK adapt to its new,
OL,12,Fwarmer climate?
OL,14,FOne of the biggest challenges is
OL,15,Fhousing.
OL,17,FHomes in the UK were built for a much
OL,18,Fcooler climate, and therefore, most
OL,19,Fhouses keep heat in.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
