OL,6,FWith increasingly hot summers, this
OL,7,Fcan lead to stifling indoor
OL,8,Ftemperatures.
OL,10,FThe UK is also experiencing more
OL,11,F'tropical nights' where temperatures
OL,12,Fdo not fall below 20C, meaning the
OL,13,Funcomfortable heat can last well into
OL,14,Fthe early hours.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
