OL,3,CHow heatwaves are changing the face of
OL,4,CBritain
OL,6,FOne solution to this is air
OL,7,Fconditioning - just 5% of homes in
OL,8,FBritain have air conditioning,
OL,9,Fcompared to a European average of 20%
OL,10,Fand 90% in the United States. But
OL,11,Faccording to some companies, uptake is
OL,12,Frising.
OL,14,FLee Ramsay, who installs air
OL,15,Fconditioning in homes and businesses
OL,16,Fand has seen his customer base triple.
OL,18,F"I've been doing this for 30 years now.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
