OL,3,CHow heatwaves are changing the face of
OL,4,CBritain
OL,6,F"When I first started, we didn't
OL,7,Finstall anything in domestics, not at
OL,8,Fall. Now I'd say it's probably making
OL,9,Fup about 40% of my business.
OL,11,F"So you know, it's absolutely
OL,12,Fbrilliant for us. But this is every
OL,13,Fyear, especially in the last eight
OL,14,Fyears, it is just increased so much."
OL,16,FThe climate is also affecting which
OL,17,Fcrops we can grow.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
