OL,3,CHow heatwaves are changing the face of
OL,4,CBritain
OL,6,FIn 2023, the UK surpassed the
OL,7,Fmilestone of 1,000 wineries with the
OL,8,Fequivalent of 21.6 million bottles of
OL,9,Fwine being produced.
OL,11,FIt continues to be a booming industry,
OL,12,Fas the warming climate is making the
OL,13,FUK more suitable for grape-growing.
OL,15,FIt is not just vineyards; some farmers
OL,16,Fare seeing conditions improve for
OL,17,Fother hotter-weather crops, including
OL,18,Folives and citrus plants.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
