OL,3,CHow heatwaves are changing the face of
OL,4,CBritain
OL,6,FAt the Citrus Centre in Sussex, they
OL,7,Fhave been growing citrus plants for
OL,8,Fthree decades, but usually they keep
OL,9,Fthem indoors and under cover for most
OL,10,Fof the year.
OL,12,FAs the climate heats up, though, they
OL,13,Fare spending more and more time
OL,14,Foutside.
OL,16,F"From Easter till now, we didn't bring
OL,17,Fthem in," says owner Chris Dennis.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
