OL,3,CHow heatwaves are changing the face of
OL,4,CBritain
OL,6,F"Usually, it's mid-May, we put plants
OL,7,Foutside hoping to keep them out, but
OL,8,Fready to bring them in if it's going
OL,9,Fto be frosty.
OL,11,F"But this year we've never put them
OL,12,Fout so early and not brought them in
OL,13,Fagain."
