OL,3,CHow heatwaves are changing the face of
OL,4,CBritain
OL,6,FAs the UK's climate heats up, we will
OL,7,Fsee hotter summers, milder winters,
OL,8,Fand increased extreme weather events
OL,9,Flike flooding or drought.
OL,11,FOur infrastructure is also under
OL,12,Fpressure.
OL,14,FThe UK is currently building nine new
OL,15,Freservoirs to help increase our water
OL,16,Fstorage, particularly during drier
OL,17,Fyears.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
