OL,6,FMeanwhile, Network Rail is currently
OL,7,Fworking on making its network more
OL,8,Fresilient to climate change by
OL,9,Fbuilding flood protection for areas of
OL,10,Fits tracks.
OL,12,FThe change in our climate will mean
OL,13,Freal changes to how we live our lives.
